-- Some China Banks Loosened Mortgage Lending Standards, Credit Suisse Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-12T02:03:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/some-china-banks-loosened-mortgage-lending-standards-credit-suisse-says.html

          
          
             Some Chinese banks have loosened
their standards for mortgage lending, at least on a case-by-case
basis, according to Credit Suisse Group AG in a report today.  
 The brokerage cited its interviews over the weekend with
more than 10 property agents and bank representatives.  
